But since the concourse at a wedding loves Fescennine songs‚ and also that well- known form of merriment furnishes an old-established precedent for freedom of speech, the remaining se- crets also, of bedchamber and couch, will be divulged in a selection from the same author, so that I have to blush twice over, since I make Virgil also immodest.
